"3 cups uncooked farfalle (bow tie pasta) (about 8 ounces)","1/3 cup fresh orange juice","1/4 cup fresh lemon juice","2 tablespoons extravirgin olive oil","1 tablespoon stone-ground mustard","2 teaspoons sugar","1 1/4 teaspoons salt","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1 1/2 teaspoons rice vinegar","2 cups shredded cooked chicken breast (about 2 breasts)","1 1/2 cups seedless red grapes, halved","1 cup thin diagonally cut celery","1/3 cup finely chopped red onion","1/3 cup coarsely chopped walnuts, toasted","3 tablespoons chopped fresh chives","2 tablespoons chopped fresh parsley"